{"id": 1934, "genre": 1001, "title": "日常生活中，什么样的距离会让你觉得太远了？", "description": "你在心理上很难接受什么样的距离？", "record_count": 2925, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170929105033YPhpAgobCqe1Vw6l.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-02T17:00:28Z", "options": [{"id": 239872, "content": "内急时却得知最近厕所要走一段路?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112285}, {"id": 243456, "content": "我脚下的球 和对手的球框", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825049}, {"id": 239873, "content": "闹钟七点，六点被尿憋醒，觉得爬起来走几步去洗手间再睡太远了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1026212}, {"id": 239874, "content": "我看着你，你看着手机，\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1117886}, {"id": 240898, "content": "加班后公交站到家门口的距离", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079810}, {"id": 239875, "content": "关键是看忙不忙啊，胡思乱想的过程基本感觉不到走了多久...其次就是对路的熟悉程度了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146614}, {"id": 240387, "content": "表情 抱抱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148373}, {"id": 239876, "content": "微博评论不回复！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294571}, {"id": 239621, "content": "到地铁口发现没带交通卡，回家拿的路途真是遥远。。。其实就500米而已。", "image": null, "praise_count": 470, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084835}, {"id": 239877, "content": "上学的距离。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146559}, {"id": 239622, "content": "长途卧铺火车", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367752}, {"id": 239878, "content": "两个人对彼此很好，却谁都不说：我喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146650}, {"id": 239623, "content": "闺蜜明明就在隔壁写字楼 中午午休那会要约个外卖都觉得远 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 862217}, {"id": 239879, "content": "不被理解的心灵", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145415}, {"id": 241159, "content": "坐在我身边视线穿我而过……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1151285}, {"id": 239624, "content": "鸡同鸭讲 无法让面前的人了解自己的初衷", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142706}, {"id": 239880, "content": "每天倒垃圾的那段路无比遥远", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1115926}, {"id": 240136, "content": "喜欢的人在自己面前，而她却不知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147470}, {"id": 239625, "content": "上坡就远 下坡就近 尤其骑车", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146112}, {"id": 239627, "content": "从3楼走下来再走回去都算远", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 846538}, {"id": 239883, "content": "尿急而又无处可撒！去哪都远", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060862}, {"id": 240395, "content": "坐地铁，手机没电的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123342}, {"id": 239628, "content": "就隔一面墙，而我却不想再见。因为回忆里的人还是不要再见了，不然回忆也没有了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146117}, {"id": 239884, "content": "手机没电，着急上厕所的时候，我拼命奔跑，目的地怎么那么遥远", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1040580}, {"id": 239630, "content": "广州到南昌的距离，一两个月见一面，却越来越陌生", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146129}, {"id": 239886, "content": "等待回答 发现对方根本没在意的时候吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 581967}, {"id": 240654, "content": "伸手握手的时候，对方没有看见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896039}, {"id": 239631, "content": "走到車邊，才發現車鑰匙在樓上家裡，真的很不想去拿啊⋯⋯", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060310}, {"id": 238864, "content": "周末宅居的时候，下楼1米都算远，即便出门就是饭店也要点外卖", "image": null, "praise_count": 147, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 239632, "content": "从心到心的距离太远了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1024309}, {"id": 239633, "content": "和自己喜欢的人说话，对方却爱睬不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 392, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097136}, {"id": 239889, "content": "卫生间和床的距离与当季气温成反比。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 425162}, {"id": 240145, "content": "明明两个人很熟悉，却要装作陌生人。擦肩而过", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1124397}, {"id": 238866, "content": "租房的时候离地铁站1公里还能接受，1.5就太远了，下雨天的话600米就吃不消了", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 239890, "content": "躺沙发上想要拿茶几上遥控器的距离。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1141789}, {"id": 238867, "content": "超过30分钟从家到公司就算远", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 239891, "content": "取外卖的距离", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146698}, {"id": 238868, "content": "平时还好，要折回家去拿东西，就觉得路途极为遥远", "image": null, "praise_count": 299, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 239636, "content": "生病在家快递死活不送，抛出一句今天货多扔门卫了自己去取吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146135}, {"id": 239892, "content": "不知道我在你心里是否是特别的那一个。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140909}, {"id": 239637, "content": "午睡的时候明明已经躺下了却突然尿急，到卫生间的距离真是遥不可及。", "image": null, "praise_count": 353, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146137}, {"id": 239893, "content": "她就在我身边，但是却不能在一起。这才是最遥远的距离吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137273}, {"id": 240149, "content": "游戏在一个点死了回存档点重新来，或者忘存档了 就是灾难啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900957}, {"id": 239638, "content": "和最亲爱的人只相隔600米左右，却再也不能去她楼下找她", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146147}, {"id": 239894, "content": "知道对方说谎的时候，感觉特别陌生", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146706}, {"id": 239639, "content": "刚开学到明年暑假的时间 让我觉得太远了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144986}, {"id": 239895, "content": "下楼取外卖的距离", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146698}, {"id": 239640, "content": "梦想与现实的距离。", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146152}, {"id": 239896, "content": "没有感情的婚姻，两个人的关系好比宇宙的东边和西边；", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1061841}, {"id": 239642, "content": "家住六楼，跑下楼后发现忘拿东西，再上去的这段路感觉最远。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921908}]}